title: Windows 7 Pro SP1 HP OEM 64bit
description:
This is an exact copy of my Windows 7 SP1 HP OEM 64bit disk. Didn't see one listed, so I decided to upload mine. ISO extracted using Brasero on Manjaro Linux.  Now that manufacturers charge for these, it's important that this community puts these out there free of charge...the way it should be!

I also have HP Windows 8.1 pro and Dell Windows 8 home. Let me know if you want those.
